com.salesforce.omakase.broadcast.annotation

Annotation Type Observe


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=METHOD)
public @interface Observe
    Use this annotation to subscribe to Syntax objects when the method will not change any aspect of the CSS or object.

    The one an only parameter for methods with this annotation should be one of the Syntax types.

    Currently, this annotation is equivalent to Rework, with a clearer indication of the intended effect of the method. This equivalence with Rework may change in the future, so take care to annotate properly.
